            <h3 class="cont_title">Open cash account in ACB</h3>
            <h4 class="cont_subtitle">GUIDELINE ON OPENING A BANK ACCOUNT AT ACB TO <br>PERFORM SECURITIES TRANSACTIONS </h4>
            <p>
                To provide more choices of investor’s cash account management as stipulated in Article 50 of Circular 210/2012/TT-BTC <br>
                guidance on the establishment and operation of securities companies issued on November 30 2012, the Company <br>
                has been associated with the ACB to deploy the service Management of investor’s cash account at ACB
            </p>
            <h5 class="sub_title">REGISTRATION PROCEDURES</h5>
            <p>(For investors who had securities trading accounts at the Company)</p>
            <table class="table_style_01">
                <caption>registration procedures : table</caption>
                <colgroup>
                    <col width="25%" />
                    <col />
                </colgroup>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">1.<br>Domestic individual<br>customers</th>
                        <td>
                            <ul class="data_list type_02">
                                <li>Letter of recommendation for bank account opening</li>
                                <li>Request for account opening and services (ACB’s form)</li>
                                <li>The original or a notarized copy of the identity card / passport</li>
                                <li>Power of attorney for the company to query account information, blockade, release money on account, transfer money from customer's account to Company's account when matching buy order (the tripartite agreement)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">2.<br />Foreign individual<br />customers</th>
                        <td>
                            <ul class="data_list type_02">
                                <li>Letter of recommendation for bank account opening</li>
                                <li>Request for account opening and services (ACB’s form)</li>
                                <li>The original or a notarized copy of permanent residence card or temporary residence card</li>
                                <li>The original or a notarized copy of the valid passport, visa</li>
                                <li>The original or a notarized copy of document proving the status of the representative, the legal guardian of the minor, people who lost their civil act capacity, people with limited capacity of civil acts (if any)</li>
                                <li>Power of attorney of foreign customer for the Company having full rights to perform transactions on current account.</li>
                                <li>Request to convert foreign currency into Vietnam Dong</li>
                            </ul>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">3.<br />Domestic institutional<br />customers</th>
                        <td>
                            <ul class="data_list type_02">
                                <li>Letter of recommendation for bank account opening</li>
                                <li>Application for account information (ACB’s form)</li>
                                <li>A notarized copy of business registration.</li>
                                <li>A notarized copy of tax code registration</li>
                                <li>A notarized copy of establishment decision/license (if any)</li>
                                <li>Identity card / passport of the legal representative</li>
                                <li>Decision on appointment of Director, Chief Accountant</li>
                                <li>Identity card / passport of Chief Accountant</li>
                                <li>The authorization papers and identity card / passport of the authorized person (if any)</li>
                                <li>The tripartite agreement.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row">4.<br />Foreign institutional<br />customers</th>
                        <td>
                            <ul class="data_list type_02">
                                <li>Letter of recommendation for bank account opening</li>
                                <li>Application for account information (ACB’s form)</li>
                                <li>Documents proving the legal establishment of the organization
                                    <ul class="data_list type_03">
                                        <li>A notarized copy of the investment license</li>
                                        <li>A notarized copy of tax code registration</li>
                                        <li>Papers proving status of the legal representative of account holder (as defined of ACB)</li>
                                        <li>A notarized copy of charter company</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>A notarized copy of passport of the legal representative or the authorized person (if any)</li>
                                <li>The tripartite agreement.</li>
                                <li>Request to convert foreign currency into Vietnam Dong.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="support_note">
                                <em>Note</em><br />
                                <p>* Records and documents specified in foreign language must be translated into Vietnamese and legalized at the Consular.</p>
                                <p>* Regulations on account opening may vary according to the regulations and policies of ACB in each period.</p>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
